WEBVTT

00:01.500 --> 00:03.600
《越狱》前情回顾
Previously onPrison Break

00:03.970 --> 00:05.010
关于那个人
There's something about this guy.

00:05.010 --> 00:06.210
他似乎知道
It's like he knows where

00:06.210 --> 00:08.280
我们要去哪里和我们在想什么 如果是真的话
we're going and what we're thinking. If that's true,

00:08.280 --> 00:11.850
不久他就能发现在犹他的钱...
it's just a matter of time before he finds out about the money in Utah

00:11.850 --> 00:13.880
我们怎么去墨西哥...
our way into Mexico...

00:13.880 --> 00:15.310
所有事
Everything.

00:20.850 --> 00:21.880
...会有律师
...have an attorney present

00:21.880 --> 00:23.250
出现在现在或者将来质询过程中
during questioning now or in the future...

00:23.250 --> 00:24.850
凯若琳 他们正带她进去
Caroline,they're taking her in.

00:24.850 --> 00:26.750
当然  我会看着她
Of course. I'll keep an eye on her.

00:26.750 --> 00:28.680
你确实做了 爸爸
You did it,Dad.

00:28.680 --> 00:30.250
像我说的那样做
Just do as you're told.

00:30.250 --> 00:32.810
不然结果会
Otherwise there will be consequences

00:32.810 --> 00:34.250
牵涉到我们两个人
that will affect us all.

00:34.250 --> 00:35.980
我爸是空军上校
My dad's an Air Force colonel.

00:35.980 --> 00:40.110
当我告诉他我和一个男孩子在一个旅馆里
When I told him I was staying in a hotel with a guy that I

00:40.110 --> 00:41.780
而且是一个我有点喜欢的男孩子
maybe sorta liked,

00:41.780 --> 00:43.910
他勃然大怒了
he lost it.

00:43.910 --> 00:46.410
你在这里干什么? 玛丽克鲁兹在哪儿?
What are you doing here? Where's Maricruz?

00:46.410 --> 00:47.580
她现在和我在一起了
She's with me now.

00:47.580 --> 00:48.910
告诉我她在哪儿
Don't push it.

00:48.910 --> 00:51.050
嘿  费尔南多  慢点
Hey,Fernando,slow down,man.

00:51.050 --> 00:55.300
我刚才正想告诉你  婚礼在拉斯维加斯举行
I was trying to tell you,the wedding is in Vegas.

00:55.310 --> 00:57.180
这会是谁?
Which one of them was it?

00:57.180 --> 00:58.210
可能是斯科菲尔德
Might be Scofield.

00:58.210 --> 00:59.310
我们还可能
Probably gonna find

00:59.310 --> 01:02.200
在这里找到他哥哥的尸体
his brother in there,too.

01:02.210 --> 01:03.180
去哪儿 先生?
Where to,sir?

01:03.180 --> 01:05.510
犹他
Utah.

01:13.080 --> 01:15.750
今天早上伊利诺斯州有关部门
This morning,authorities in Illinois

01:15.750 --> 01:17.950
发布了关于越狱最新情况
issued an update on the escaped convicts

01:17.950 --> 01:20.580
到现在为止  从福克斯河越狱的八个人中
known until now as the Fox River Eight

01:20.580 --> 01:22.550
芝加哥黑帮老大约翰 阿布鲁奇
Chicago mob boss John Abruzzi

01:22.550 --> 01:26.950
昨晚在华盛顿一家汽车旅馆外被击毙
was gunned down outside a Washington D.C. motel last night

01:26.950 --> 01:28.910
是由于调查人员获得了线人的消息
after investigators received a tip from an informant.

01:28.910 --> 01:30.080
其余七人仍旧在逃
The other seven escapees

01:30.080 --> 01:32.750
依然极度危险
are still at large and considered dangerous.

01:36.550 --> 01:39.350
我没想到阿布鲁奇会是第一个
I didn't think Abruzzi'd be the first to go.

01:39.350 --> 01:42.180
我觉得一定还会有很多意外的事情
I have a feeling we're in for lots of surprises.

01:42.180 --> 01:44.380
他们说我们还有七个人
They said seven are still out there.

01:44.380 --> 01:45.880
看来我们伪造死亡被识破了
So much for faking our deaths.

01:45.880 --> 01:48.550
我们赢得了一些时间  所以还是有价值的
I bought us some time-- that's what counts.

01:51.820 --> 01:53.120
还有多远?
How much further?

01:53.120 --> 01:54.480
七八十英里
70,80 miles.

01:54.480 --> 01:56.480
好的 我们下午就能到KK农场了
Good. Means we should be hitting the Double K Ranch by this afternoon. Or we can keep driving,

01:56.480 --> 01:58.580
我们可以接上LJ
pick up LJ

01:58.580 --> 01:59.920
然后一直开到巴拿马
and hit Panama.

01:59.920 --> 02:01.080
我们不能去巴拿马
We can't hit Panama!

02:01.080 --> 02:03.450
我们哪儿都不能去  什么都不能做
We can't hit anything! We can't do anything

02:03.450 --> 02:04.450
在没有钱的情况下
without the money.

02:04.450 --> 02:06.390
我们要找到查尔斯藏钱的地方
We need to find Charles's stash.

02:08.080 --> 02:10.730
我知道其他人也在想着这事
I know some other guys who are thinking the same thing.

02:13.480 --> 02:19.620
钱就埋在KK农场的一个地窖里
The money is buried under a silo at the Double K Ranch

02:19.620 --> 02:23.550
就在犹他州的图勒镇外
just outside of Tooele,Utah.

02:40.440 --> 02:41.210
查票
Tickets?

02:43.350 --> 02:45.650
哦  在夏延的时候
Oh. Um,you know,when I was in Cheyenne,

02:45.650 --> 02:47.820
我从口袋里把票拿出来的时候
I pulled my ticket out of the bag.

02:47.820 --> 02:49.650
把它撕成了两半...
It tore in half,and...

02:49.650 --> 02:51.750
我不知道另一半哪儿去了
I have no idea what happened to the other part.

02:51.750 --> 02:53.980
他们没有补给你一张新的?
They didn't issue you a replacement?

02:53.980 --> 02:57.080
没有啊 那位小姐  好像叫雪莉
No. The young lady-- I think-- her name was Sherry--

02:57.080 --> 02:58.980
说剩下这半张也能用
she actually said that this half is okay

02:58.980 --> 03:00.520
因为上面的条形码还在
because the bar code is on it.

03:00.520 --> 03:02.620
但是你确实是需要一张完整的票
Well,you really need the whole ticket.

03:02.620 --> 03:05.550
我当时就是想要避免这样的情况
This is exactly what I was trying to avoid.

03:05.550 --> 03:08.150
但是她说  没问题的...
She said that everything would be fine because...

03:08.150 --> 03:09.350
好吧  现在算了
That's okay. It'll do for now.

03:09.350 --> 03:11.480
不过你务必要换一张新的
But make sure you ask for a replacement

03:11.480 --> 03:12.480
当你到了普罗沃后
when you get to Provo.

03:12.480 --> 03:13.930
我一定会的  谢谢
I definitely will. Thank you.

03:15.220 --> 03:17.520
总会遇到些事情 是吧?
It's always something,huh?

03:17.520 --> 03:18.310
哦 是的 我明白
Oh,God,I know.

03:30.080 --> 03:33.820
我不想回家了

03:33.820 --> 03:35.950
我真想我们就这样一直开车走
I wish we could keep driving.

03:35.950 --> 03:38.590
我可不觉得你老爸会同意的
I don't think your Pops will be down for that.

03:40.030 --> 03:41.030
这样不是很有趣吗?
Wouldn't it be fun?

03:42.850 --> 03:44.900
我们可以去...
We could go to...

03:45.250 --> 03:46.510
夏威夷?
Hawaii?

03:46.520 --> 03:47.750
哈 你不能
Yo,you can't

03:47.750 --> 03:50.570
开车去夏威夷
drive to Hawaii.

03:50.580 --> 03:51.580
我知道
I know.

03:51.580 --> 03:53.250
我只是说说
I'm just saying

03:53.250 --> 03:54.260
我希望
I wish.

03:56.180 --> 03:58.120
呃
Whoa,whoa.

03:58.120 --> 04:00.020
不...不要去开 他们会走的
No,no. Don't get it. They'll leave.

04:00.020 --> 04:01.490
我只是看看是谁
Just let me see who it is

04:07.750 --> 04:08.750
是个警察
It's a cop.

04:09.140 --> 04:11.080
不 不 不 不 不
No,no,no,no,no. Whoa,whoa,whoa.

04:13.820 --> 04:16.120
很抱歉打扰你  小姐
Sorry to disturb you,ma'am.

04:16.120 --> 04:17.560
你有没有见过这个人?
Have you happened to see this person?

04:54.760 --> 04:56.250
昨天晚上我们收到线索
Last night we got a few phone calls

04:56.250 --> 04:57.790
说他在这附近出现
that he was spotted in the area.

04:57.790 --> 04:59.490
所以我们在挨家挨户地调查
So we're going door-to-door.

05:00.870 --> 05:01.880
你们为什么要找他?
Why are you looking for him?

05:02.250 --> 05:03.840
他一两天前
He escaped from prison in Illinois

05:03.850 --> 05:05.010
从伊利诺斯州一所监狱越狱
a couple of days ago.

05:05.010 --> 05:06.280
你有没有见过他?
And you see him?

05:11.900 --> 05:12.570
没有
No.

05:13.470 --> 05:14.700
没见过
He doesn't look familiar.

05:15.860 --> 05:16.590
你确定?
Are you sure?

05:18.590 --> 05:19.490
是的  我确定
Yeah. I'm sure.

05:22.880 --> 05:23.390
好吧
All right.

05:23.680 --> 05:24.480
谢谢 打扰你了
Thanks for your time.

05:30.750 --> 05:31.970
呃
Whoa.

05:32.440 --> 05:33.390
嘿 嘿
Whoa,whoa,whoa.

05:33.400 --> 05:34.250
这不是...
This ain't...

05:34.250 --> 05:36.180
不是你想的那样 好吗?
This is not what you think,all right?

05:36.180 --> 05:37.000
嘿
Look.

05:37.910 --> 05:38.740
听我说 这...
Listen to me,this...

05:39.250 --> 05:40.420
听...我说
Just... listen.

05:41.240 --> 05:41.900
好吗?
Okay?

05:42.640 --> 05:43.550
我仅仅只是
All I did

05:43.550 --> 05:45.320
偷了一张棒球卡
was steal a baseball card.

05:46.300 --> 05:48.150
好吗? 我并不像那儿的其他人
Okay? I'm not like those other fools up in there.

05:50.730 --> 05:53.010
我现在想去散个步 难道不行么?
I'm gonna go for a walk,okay?

05:54.480 --> 05:55.910
听着... 我会把我的钥匙留这儿
Listen... I'm gonna leave my keys right here.

05:57.330 --> 05:58.480
等到我回来的时候
And when I come back,

05:59.420 --> 06:00.470
我的车子自然会不见
my car will be gone.

06:01.890 --> 06:02.530
我想
I'm sure,

06:03.190 --> 06:03.960
几个小时后
in a few hours,

06:04.810 --> 06:05.870
警察会在某个地方找到它的...
they'll find it somewhere...

06:07.440 --> 06:08.240
被扔在了路边
abandoned.

06:14.110 --> 06:15.200
等等  等等
Wait. Wait.

06:22.110 --> 06:23.400
我也不希望我现在这样子
I wish it could be different.

06:25.510 --> 06:26.760
我得走了
I have to go.

06:46.930 --> 06:47.520
这就是图雷
"Too-le."

06:48.190 --> 06:49.410
我想应该是图勒镇
I think it's "To-ill-uh."

06:50.170 --> 06:50.910
这么个小镇
Hell of a town.

06:51.650 --> 06:52.710
小点好
Small is good.

06:52.710 --> 06:54.510
那个农场找起来就容易点
Means the ranch'll be easier to find.

06:54.510 --> 06:56.610
我们要做的就是拿到钱
All we got to do is get that money

06:57.920 --> 06:59.160
然后在日落前离开
and we'll be out of here by nightfall.

06:59.630 --> 07:00.370
对
Right.

07:21.150 --> 07:23.710
哦 长官 斯科菲尔德的车祸化验报告出来了
Oh,sir. Soil test came back from Scofield's crash.

07:23.710 --> 07:26.250
不用进一步的证明
Not that you need any more proof,but...

07:26.250 --> 07:28.150
他现在还逍遥法外
he really went out of his way this time.

07:28.150 --> 07:30.180
还有什么消息?
What else do you have?

07:30.180 --> 07:32.210
内布拉斯加州有人被暴力攻击
Man was violently assaulted in Nebraska

07:32.210 --> 07:34.550
根据搭车旅行者的描述 像是帝博格干的
by a hitchhiker matching Bagwell's description.

07:34.550 --> 07:36.010
他正在沿着80州际公路往西逃
He was headed west on the I-80.

07:36.010 --> 07:38.110
俄马哈把照片排好了
Omaha's putting together a photo lineup.

07:38.490 --> 07:39.600
有什么关于斯科菲尔德的?
What do you have on Scofield?

07:40.650 --> 07:41.470
其他人有没有
What does anybody

07:41.470 --> 07:42.660
关于斯科菲尔德的消息?
have on Scofield?

07:44.110 --> 07:45.710
嗯 我从他的硬盘里
Uh,I've got some results

07:45.710 --> 07:46.980
得到了些信息
from his hard drive.

07:46.980 --> 07:49.310
就是从河里打捞上来的那个硬盘
The one recovered from the river.

07:50.700 --> 07:51.420
我们可以运用
We were able to use

07:51.430 --> 07:53.290
扇形编辑器去恢复主要信息
the sector editor to restore the master boot.

07:53.620 --> 07:54.220
然后...
So from that...

07:54.220 --> 07:55.460
我不管你怎么做的
I don't care how you did it.

07:55.470 --> 07:56.200
你找到了什么?
What do you have?

07:58.810 --> 08:00.510
超过一半的缓冲容量
More than half the contents of the buffer.

08:00.510 --> 08:01.760
接近百分之60
About 60%.

08:08.370 --> 08:09.320
但分布都很零散
It looks pretty random.

08:09.330 --> 08:11.620
全部打印出来  放到我桌子上
Print it up. All of it. I want it on my desk.

08:15.480 --> 08:16.650
呃  你猜怎么着?
Well,guess what?

08:18.460 --> 08:20.220
列表上没有KK农场
No listing for a Double K Ranch.

08:21.260 --> 08:21.950
请问
Excuse me.

08:22.290 --> 08:23.750
你知道KK农场在哪儿吗?
You know where I might find a Double K Ranch?

08:23.760 --> 08:25.010
什么?
What you call it?

08:25.400 --> 08:26.690
KK农场
Double K Ranch.

08:26.690 --> 08:27.510
不知道
No.

08:28.090 --> 08:28.950
你是这一带的人么?
You from around here?

08:28.950 --> 08:30.460
是的  从小到大一直在这
Yeah. Born and raised.

08:30.870 --> 08:32.210
没有什么KK什么农场
There's no Double-nothin'.

08:32.630 --> 08:33.700
好了  谢谢
Great. Thank you.

08:36.470 --> 08:37.330
看来韦斯特莫兰德在临死前
Looks like Westmoreland

08:37.340 --> 08:39.610
耍了你一通
spent his last breath blowing smoke up your ass.

08:39.610 --> 08:41.080
还有个方法
There's one way to find out.

08:41.540 --> 08:43.240
这个县一定会保存有财产记录
The county keeps property records.

08:44.010 --> 08:45.650
上面会用标尺标明所有地点
Every plot is mapped out

08:45.650 --> 08:47.350
是公共档案
with dimensions. It's public record.

08:47.970 --> 08:50.560
如果这里有财税办公室的话
But if there is a tax assessor's office here,

08:51.910 --> 08:55.380
那一定是在这里 市政大楼
it's gonna be in there,the Municipal Building.

08:57.120 --> 08:58.540
那里有警察巡逻的

09:03.730 --> 09:04.420
快讯
Dispatch.

09:04.730 --> 09:07.760
有人...有人今天早上偷走了我的车
Someone...someone stole my car this morning.

09:08.120 --> 09:10.060
我在莲花汽车旅馆  80州际公路上
I'm at the Lotus Motel off Interstate 80

09:10.060 --> 09:11.360
你有没有看到是谁偷走的?
Did you see who took it?

09:11.680 --> 09:13.740
没有  我出去散步了
No. I went out for a walk

09:13.750 --> 09:15.820
回来的时候  已经不见了
and when I came back,it was gone.

09:15.820 --> 09:16.470
今天早上?
This morning?

09:16.930 --> 09:17.930
为什么之前不打电话来?
Why didn't you call before?

09:17.930 --> 09:19.920
我... 我也不知道
I... I don't know.

09:54.850 --> 09:57.090
哈罗!

10:12.720 --> 10:15.290
芝加哥伊利诺州

10:18.080 --> 10:19.180
克里曼先生
Mr. Kellerman.

10:19.190 --> 10:20.100
金姆先生
Mr. Kim.

10:22.380 --> 10:23.940
能在芝加哥见到你 真是巧啊
Surprised to see you in Chicago.

10:25.080 --> 10:26.170
只是来看下进展
Just looking for updates.

10:26.170 --> 10:27.620
唐克雷蒂 莎拉  我正在处理
Sara Tancredi. I'm on it.

10:28.700 --> 10:30.560
你就花了你所有的时间去追查她?
Is pursuing her the best use of your time?

10:30.560 --> 10:31.510
没错
It is.

10:32.160 --> 10:33.330
她和斯科菲尔德还有联系
She's in contact with Scofield.

10:33.340 --> 10:34.870
昨天他们通电话的时候我就在旁边
I was there when he called yesterday.

10:35.740 --> 10:37.430
我们有了她  就能找到斯科菲尔德
We stay with her,she takes us right to him,

10:37.920 --> 10:39.010
找到斯科菲尔德  就找到布伦斯
he takes us to Burrows.

10:40.640 --> 10:41.300
得了
All right.

10:42.260 --> 10:43.120
既然你那么自信
If you're that confident.

10:43.430 --> 10:44.070
是的
I am.

10:46.080 --> 10:47.090
我会告诉总统
I'll let the president know.

10:47.100 --> 10:48.950
我会直接和总统联系
I contact the president directly.

10:51.000 --> 10:52.090
我来联系她
I'll contact her.

10:54.170 --> 10:54.980
有任何进展通知我一下
Keep me posted.

11:21.120 --> 11:23.630
如果你要找回你的尊严
If you want to restore your dignity,

11:23.630 --> 11:25.160
你就必须做出行动
you need to take action.

11:25.160 --> 11:29.760
痛改前非不仅仅是说句对不起就行了
Making amends requires much more than saying "I'm sorry."

11:29.760 --> 11:32.290
你需要学着改变自己
It means learning to change.

11:32.290 --> 11:35.060
道歉只是第一步
The apology is just the first step.

11:35.060 --> 11:38.700
最重要的是在你道歉的时候
The most important thing is that you display honesty,

11:38.700 --> 11:41.300
你必须诚实
courage and compassion

11:41.300 --> 11:43.770
要有勇气和同情心
when you extend your apologies.

11:43.770 --> 11:46.700
你要做的就是去赢得别人的原谅
You need to earn your forgiveness.

11:46.700 --> 11:48.650
我们星期五再继续讨论
We'll talk about it more on Friday.

12:03.610 --> 12:04.880
我有个好主意
I've got a great idea.

12:04.880 --> 12:06.510
怎么说?
What's that?

12:06.510 --> 12:08.050
既然你那么喜欢
Since you are such a fan

12:08.050 --> 12:10.750
外面买的蓝莓派
of lame,store-bought blueberry pie,

12:10.750 --> 12:14.320
我打算今晚亲自做个你喜欢的给你
I am going to bake you a real pie of your choice tonight.

12:17.010 --> 12:20.000
不用了
I can't.

12:20.010 --> 12:22.350
现在除了我的医生外
I really don't need to be seeing anyone right now

12:22.350 --> 12:23.820
我真的不想见任何人
who isn't my therapist.

12:25.310 --> 12:27.460
我最近也像个隐居者
I've been a hermit lately,too.

12:28.980 --> 12:30.850
我的搭档丹尼尔外出谈生意去了
My partner Daniel's away on business.

12:30.850 --> 12:33.080
每晚我都独自一人
I've been sitting around every night by myself.

12:33.080 --> 12:35.050
有点可怜啊
Kind of pathetic.

