39:09.370 --> 39:11.190
他把钱藏在他经过的某个地方了
he got rid of it somewhere along the way.

39:11.190 --> 39:13.900
等等 等等 这是事实? 你发现了这一切?
Wait,wait,this is fact? You figured all this out?

39:13.900 --> 39:15.520
不是  是斯科菲尔德发现的
No. Scofield did.

39:15.530 --> 39:17.310
这就是为什么他会带着这个老头一起
That's why he was bringing the old man along.

39:17.320 --> 39:18.580
那些钱在犹他州
The money's in Utah.

39:18.580 --> 39:19.900
所以他们都要去那里
And they're all going to get it.

39:24.740 --> 39:26.150
你知道吗?在...泰国
You know,in,uh,Thailand

39:26.150 --> 39:27.850
他们有个黑市
they got a black market

39:27.850 --> 39:29.680
那里你能做任何外科手术
where you can get any kind of surgery you need,

39:29.690 --> 39:30.950
甚至手的移植
even a hand transplant.

39:31.420 --> 39:32.990
你有毛病 你知道吗?  继续开
You're sick,you know that. Keep going.

39:33.000 --> 39:34.640
转弯处就在这儿附近什么地方
The turnoff's just up here somewhere.

39:35.480 --> 39:36.710
过不过那小路?
Before or after Sheep Road?

39:39.470 --> 39:40.900
怎么了 你忘记了?
What's the matter,Theodore,did you forget?

39:40.910 --> 39:42.860
我怎么会忘记那小路的?
How could I forget a road called Sheep?

39:42.860 --> 39:43.750
过的
It's after.

39:44.160 --> 39:45.820
你们不觉得心里很暖吗?
Don't you feel all warm inside

39:45.830 --> 39:46.860
现在我们在一起了
now that we're working together?

39:46.860 --> 39:48.250
我们不是在一起
We aren't working together.

39:48.890 --> 39:50.190
你在这里只是借你的一只手而已
You're just here to lend a hand.

39:50.200 --> 39:51.730
好了 减速
Now,slow down.

39:51.740 --> 39:53.550
就在那里 那条小路
That was it,that little bitty road

39:53.560 --> 39:54.370
后退
right back there.

40:18.240 --> 40:19.270
离这还有多远?
How far is it from here?

40:19.890 --> 40:22.700
如果我记得没错的话还有1/4英里
Quarter mile if I remember the scale properly.

40:23.320 --> 40:24.060
走吧
Start walking.

40:45.700 --> 40:46.310
法兰克?
Frank?

40:47.410 --> 40:48.460
好的 我快准备好了
Yeah,I'm almost ready.

40:49.330 --> 40:50.860
航班是几点钟?
What time did you say the flight was?

40:50.870 --> 40:51.790
8:00
8:00.

40:51.790 --> 40:53.800
听着 相比其他人
Listen,I hope you get this nomination

40:53.800 --> 40:54.930
我更希望你得到这个任命,但是...
more than anyone,but...

40:54.940 --> 40:56.300
你要准备好
be prepared.

40:56.620 --> 40:58.240
这个布伦斯的事情很棘手
This Burrows thing may steamroll.

40:58.250 --> 41:00.240
好吧 我们等着 就像你说的
Well,we'll wait it out,just like you said.

41:00.930 --> 41:02.140
问题是有很多麻烦
Problem is too many headlines.

41:02.670 --> 41:04.580
他的律师 尼克 萨维恩 已经死了
His lawyer Nick Savrinn's already dead.

41:05.170 --> 41:07.240
他的儿子由于两起谋杀案正在等候审判
His kid's awaiting trial for double homicide.

41:07.240 --> 41:09.760
而现在他的主辩律师失踪了
And now his lead counsel is classified as missing.

41:10.090 --> 41:11.640
哦,她是失踪了还是死了?
Well,is she missing or is she dead?

41:13.420 --> 41:15.870
我只是认为你在去华盛顿之前应该都想清楚
I just thought you should know before you go to Washington.

41:16.650 --> 41:18.720
布鲁斯 有什么事情和这有关?
Bruce,is there something connecting all of this?

41:19.360 --> 41:21.660
最好你不要问那么多问题
It's probably best you don't ask a whole lot of questions.

41:33.000 --> 41:33.700
现在往哪儿走?
Where now?

41:37.210 --> 41:38.100
往前直走
Right up there.

41:39.340 --> 41:41.050
这山坡就是财产的边界线
The hill borders the property.

41:41.950 --> 41:43.780
KK农场就在山的那一边
KK's on the other side.

41:44.260 --> 41:45.560
我拿到钱做的第一件事
First thing I'm gonna do with the money?

41:46.530 --> 41:47.550
买双新鞋
Buy new shoes.

41:47.550 --> 41:49.050
第二件  墨西哥玉米卷
Second thing: tacos.

41:49.050 --> 41:51.380
第三件  冰啤酒
Third thing: ice cold beer.

41:51.710 --> 41:54.050
第四件  一点牙膏
Fourth thing: a little toothpaste.

42:11.270 --> 42:11.850
马宏
Mahone.

42:11.860 --> 42:13.750
马宏长官 你的车子已经开出来了
Agent Mahone,your car's out front,sir.

42:14.570 --> 42:15.940
去犹他的航班还有1小时
The flight to Utah leaves in an hour.

42:15.950 --> 42:18.410
我就来 谢谢
I'll be there. Thank you.

42:44.980 --> 42:46.960
第九件  洗个澡
Ninth thing: a shower.

42:47.630 --> 42:49.470
第十件  睡个好觉
Tenth thing: a good night's sleep.

42:50.270 --> 42:52.640
一家好旅馆 干净的床单
A nice hotel. Clean sheets.

42:52.650 --> 42:55.140
看 树桩就是财产分界线的标志
Look,stakes marking the property line.

42:55.150 --> 42:56.480
应该到了
Should be dead ahead.

42:58.280 --> 42:59.440
看到地窖了吗?
Can you see the silo?

43:06.630 --> 43:08.030
上面重新建造过了
The bastards built over it.

43:11.020 --> 43:11.910
完了
It's gone.
